oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mural of David Craig's Fort
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Image of a mural in the Fort Craig Elementary School cafeteria painted by Joel Anderson, a Maryville High School student. The painting depicts the artist's conception of David Craig's Fort in 1785.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Forts & fortifications
